        <p style="color: #c4b5d4; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
 <p>
        As a Data Scientist currently pursuing my degree at the University of Zimbabwe, 
        I am driven by a passion for transforming raw data into strategic assets. 
        My analytical journey began at Ngezi High School, where I cultivated a deep 
        appreciation for mathematics and its power to solve complex, real-world problems.
    </p>

    <p>
        I have augmented my academic foundation with practical, high-impact experience 
        during my internship at ZIMSTAT (Zimbabwe National Statistics Agency). 
        There, I contributed to several pivotal initiatives, including the automation 
        of the Consumer Price Index (CPI) and Inflation metrics, the design of robust 
        database pipelines, and the development of a Scientific Hardship Index designed 
        to inform evidence-based policy-making.
    </p>

    <p>
        My core expertise lies in synthesizing intricate datasets to deliver clear, 
        actionable insights that not only drive business growth and operational efficiency 
        but also empower sound policy decisions.
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>My approach is anchored in the FRLSH framework:</strong>
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li><span class="highlight">Focus:</span> Zeroing in on key performance drivers to avoid data noise.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Reliability:</span> Ensuring data integrity and reproducibility through rigorous validation.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Logic:</span> Applying structured, mathematical reasoning to uncover hidden patterns.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Strategy:</span> Aligning analytical outputs with overarching business or policy objectives.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Human Impact:</span> Translating complex findings into intuitive narratives that resonate with stakeholders and drive positive change.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        I am committed to leveraging data science to catalyze sustainable development 
        and competitive advantage for Zimbabwean enterprises and institutions also specializing in turning complex data into clear, actionable insights that drive business growth 
          and inform policy decisions.
    </p>
